data.meta_description: Princess Irina Pavlovna Romanova- Paley with her only child from her first marriage to Prince Feodor Alexandrovich Romanov of Russia.The child was Prince Mikhail Feodorovich Romanov.Irina was the daughter of the Grand Duke Pavel Alexandrovich Romanov of Russia from his second marriage.Feodor was the third child of the Grand Duchess Xenia Alexandrovna Romanova of Russia and the Grand Duke Alexander Mikhailovich Romanov of Russia. "AL"
